! And here there is no transition to self-flagellation or kinks in the spirit of some publications. Even black humor and jokes below the pager are served deliciously and in moderation, rather than a stream from the machine gun a la modern comedies.</span></span></span><span style=\"color: #333333;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">\r\n\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\"color: #333333;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Keep the Mark!</span></span></span><span style=\"color: #333333;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">\r\n\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\"color: #333333;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">An excellent adult action movie with meat, black humor, self-irony and banter over everyone and everything.</span></span></span>', '', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '88-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-07-09 18:08:25', '2018-07-09 18:08:25', '', 88, 'http://localhost/philosophy/2018/07/09/88-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
